1 tomato
1 tub cream cheese
1 packet basil pesto
1 packet the everything bagel

Thinly slice tomato.

Halve the everything bagels. Toast or grill to your liking.

Transfer the toasted bagels to serving plates. Spread with cream cheese, top with tomato and dollop with basil pesto to serve.

FRESH TIP: Add a fresh herb to your bagel!